PROGRAM:
value = input("Enter something: ")

if value.isdigit():
    num = int(value)
    print("It is a number")

    if num > 0:
        print("Positive")
        if num % 2 == 0:
            print("Even")
        else:
            print("Odd")
    else:
        print("Negative")

else:
    print("Not a number, data type =", type(value))


OUTPUT:

Enter something: 14
It is a number
Positive
Even
